by foot.

This helped me respond to a friend's post I made on Facebook that my address is not 0 m^2. It is in reality not even 750 m^2, the amount of land I occupy hopefully until the day I die. Some 27 years now and counting.

Hello again. After a hearty lunch of chicken stew and rice and a bit of sleep I awoke to the servants - dad and sis - preparing for church. I went along too. I'm on vacation after all.

The 2-hour service was interesting. They had kids' choir, regular choir, several preaching sessions some of which are done in Edo, another dozed through in English and the one done in French was impressive. They also had an interactive session in French.

I've been bathroom hogging lately I know. There is just so much to share here that I have to make sacrifices.
